{"tid":438470,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"記錄下平時係出面食d乜，好食唔好食","createTime":"2017-10-17T03:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T07:07:55.000Z","uid":152612,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cebd6defcb24408aefc4ff492b6ee397acec62fa","tid":438470,"uid":152612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:04:01.000Z","msg":"小妹好鍾意食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔係成日有機會食好西<br />\n亦都唔係成日咁得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出去搵好野食<br />\n不過都想寫下出食左d乜，好食唔好食咁<br />\n<br />\n小妹住天水圍<br />\n暫時返工都係天水圍，雖然有可能會出街，但真係少，平時都好宅<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個貼既內容都係以天水圍為多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7359fefe982a96455a86fa429b0aaf76228641","tid":438470,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"pmed"},{"pid":"dcc61473a34147223bbd640cf3fd8ddc393b55ac","tid":438470,"uid":152612,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"唔知點解up唔到圖，搞左好耐，老細又返左黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/6T7dF8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F6T7dF8.jpg&h=f30b10cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/CysYrk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FCysYrk.jpg&h=81a60353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/O1qrYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FO1qrYQ.jpg&h=d60b698b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n銀座mx既桂花香檸雞扒同炒蛋配多士（外賣）<br />\n<br />\n本身個炒蛋係ok既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢唔小心撈埋左d桂花青檸汁<br />\n味道非常微妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後個雞扒<br />\n尺寸都還可以，味道就係平時食既雞扒味<br />\n汁同雞扒既味道係分開既，即係分開黎食既話係完全食唔出桂花青檸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n杯阿華田超甜，甜到飲落去好似受刑咁，仲要係我老細面前扮冇野飲落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmx比左包砂糖我，但完全冇咁既需要<br />\n<br />\n最後，個麥多士我冇試，因為冇牛油，只係咁食我食唔落<br />\n<br />\n總結一句，呢個餐，我唔會再叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f596876c9f59ac8024948b6f8248840cad94910","tid":438470,"uid":3004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:07:25.000Z","msg":"小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d7f26649012ff940a426016d994ae7ddf5cb6c","tid":438470,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:35:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab29c0fd8ba2f90cbbdc1d3880f8359d9d107852","tid":438470,"uid":152612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊食飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係附近？"},{"pid":"77a5e0488a47c95ee0367e8043d66de1a4ff743f","tid":438470,"uid":152612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"今日去左天盛既富臨<br />\n去過幾次，間野麻麻<br />\n同銀座果間比較，銀座果間會好d"},{"pid":"38aa2b3e72f170e35792d39aed3405bf0493091e","tid":438470,"uid":99257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"鐘意食燒雞翼"}]}